__ Cantrip: Exterminate ______________________ Cost: 5 ______________________

Use:  cantrip exterminate < creature >         Material Component: creature
Use:  C exterminate < creature >

The cantrip exterminate is a minor magic of the sphere of necromancy.  When
evoked, the exterminate cantrip will kill any creature with less then five 
hp.  This is generally used for eliminating small rodents or other bothersome 
(but tiny) creatures.
